1681
01:39:10.940 --> 01:39:14.810
So to summarize, we can say that we have developed a potent multimodal

1682
01:39:15.770 --> 01:39:19.370
microRNA-based therapeutics with improved efficacy and

1683
01:39:19.430 --> 01:39:23.310
delivery. And the modified microRNA mimic is potent

1684
01:39:23.590 --> 01:39:26.610
irrespective of the cell's BRCA or p53 status.

1685
01:39:27.670 --> 01:39:31.530
We also saw that it overcomes PARP inhibitor resistance and synergize

1686
01:39:31.590 --> 01:39:35.510
with PARP inhibitor olaparib, and it also demonstrates strong in

1687
01:39:35.530 --> 01:39:37.900
