1688
01:39:39.230 --> 01:39:43.130
So if we want to say how the modified microRNA works, we can say

1689
01:39:43.190 --> 01:39:45.330
that the modified microRNA goes inside the cell.

1690
01:39:45.830 --> 01:39:49.350
The guide strand gets incorporated into the

1691
01:39:49.410 --> 01:39:52.790
