1696
01:40:06.030 --> 01:40:08.970
After that, it gets degraded by 5 prime and 3 prime

1697
01:40:09.190 --> 01:40:12.880
exonucleases, which releases 5-FU, gemcitabine, and

1698
01:40:12.910 --> 01:40:16.610
methotrexate. And all of this together causes replication

1699
01:40:16.730 --> 01:40:19.870
stress and DNA damage. And in the same cell,

1700
01:40:20.370 --> 01:40:24.070
the convergence of DNA damage, checkpoint aggravation, and reduced

1701
01:40:24.090 --> 01:40:27.790
survival signaling overruns the cancer cells and

1702
01:40:27.830 --> 01:40:30.690
force towards mitotic catastrophe and apoptosis.

1703
01:40:31.270 --> 01:40:34.850
So with this modified microRNA mimic, we are trying

1704
01:40:35.470 --> 01:40:39.350
to eliminate all the rescue pathways

1705
01:40:39.390 --> 01:40:40.390
that cancer cell can

1706
01:40:42.510 --> 01:40:43.450
use to adapt.

